Â She texted... ( 21 - 20 Saints ) Â Then... ( 23 - 21 Vikings 1:29 ) Â So I figured the Saints had 1:29 to try and get in field goal range. I didn't think they would as the Vikings have a good defense this year. Â Then, 12 minutes later she texted me... ( 24 - 23 Saints ) Â I became really sad. I came to a stop sign with no one around and just put my head down. I then preceded to the house she was at, thinking about how good the vikings had done all year, and how it was all over in their first playoff game. Â I sadly sat there in the car in front of the house waiting for her to come out. Â Then, ding ding, another text.
